BNP Makes Offer to Buy Popolare Milano: F&M

-- B y   S o n i a   S i r l e t t i   a n d   T o m m a s o   E b h a r d t
-- 
2011-06-17T07:49:14Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-17/bnp-paribas-makes-all-cash-offer-to-acquire-popolare-milano-f-m-reports.html
BNP Paribas (BNP)  SA made an all-cash
offer to buy Banca Popolare di Milano Scrl, Finanza & Mercati
reported, without saying where it got the information.  Bank of Italy  may oppose the deal, the Italian daily said,
adding that the Italian lander may study a combination with
 Banca Popolare dell’Emilia Romagna Scrl. (BPE)  The newspaper didn’t
give any financial details about the offer.  Banca Popolare di Milano declined to comment on the matter.
A Rome-based spokesman for BNP Paribas didn’t immediately return
calls from Bloomberg.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Tommaso Ebhardt at 
 tebhardt@bloomberg.net  